6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Designs.ai and Stencil share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Export Formats, Stock Assets. Where Designs.ai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Brand Kit and Ai Generation and Animations, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Designs.ai holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Stencil scores 5/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Stencil comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Designs.ai begins at $29/mo. Stencil stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Designs.ai requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
